{{Infobox feature on Venus
|name= Heng-O Corona
|image=
|caption=
|type= [[Corona (planetary geology)|corona]]
|coordinates= {{coord|2|N|255|E|globe:venus_type:landmark|display=inline,title}}
|diameter=1060 km
|eponym=[[Chang'e (mythology)|Heng O]]
