'''Heng-O Corona''' is a [[Corona (planetary geology)|corona]] in [[Guinevere Planitia]] on the planet [[Venus]] at Latitude 2° North, Longitude 355° East. It has a diameter of {{convert|1060|km|mi}}, and is the 2nd largest corona on Venus.

It is named for [[Chang'e (mythology)|Heng O]] (also known as Chang'e), the Chinese goddess of the Moon. 

