GeoProof<ref>{{cite web |url=http://home.gna.org/geoproof/ |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2006-04-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060421112504/http://home.gna.org/geoproof/ |archivedate=2006-04-21 |df= }}</ref> is a free [[GNU General Public License|GPL]] dynamic geometry software, written in [[OCaml]].

